cation. Hunchmate may moderate or remove content that violates policy or legal obligations.</p></section><section class=\"legal-page__section\"><h2>4. Service Changes</h2><p>We may update, improve, or discontinue features as needed. Material changes to terms may be posted on this page, and continued use indicates acceptance of the updated terms.</p></section><section class=\"legal-page__section\"><h2>5. Contact</h2><p>For legal questions, reach us at support@hunchmate.com through the Contact page.</p></section></article></div></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"site-footer\" aria-label=\"Site footer\"><div class=\"site-footer__glow-bar\"></div><div class=\"site-footer__inner container\"><div class=\"site-footer__top\"><div class=\"site-footer__brand-col\"><a class=\"site-footer__brand-logo\" aria-label=\"Hunchmate Home\" href=\"/\"><img src=\"/_next/static/media/HUNCHMATE - Logo Pack (2).0xjy2zfzpq5od.png\" alt=\"HunchMate\"/></a><p class=\"site-footer__tagline\">Discover and attend <br/>the best hackathons &amp; tech events — all in one place.</p><div class=\"site-footer__socials\" aria-label=\"Social links\"><a href=\"https://x.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\"site-footer__social\" aria-label=\"X / Twitter\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-x\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M18 6 6 18\"></path><path d=\"m6 6 12 12\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://linkedin.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\"site-footer__social\" aria-label=\"LinkedIn\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"17\" height=\"17\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link2 lucide-link-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M9 17H7A5 5 0 0 1 7 7h2\